{"_id":"SkSP9w5gf","title":"linux 安装JDK","body":{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"ag6qs","text":"linux 安装JDK","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"59kd9","text":"一. 解压安装jdk","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"247vc","text":"在shell终端下进入jdk-6u14-linux-i586.bin文件所在目录，","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"eaqmt","text":"执行命令 ./jdk-6u14-linux-i586.bin 这时会出现一段协议，连继敲回车，当询问是否同意的时候，输入yes，回车。之后会在当前目录下生成一个jdk1.6.0_14目录，你可以将它复制到 任何一个目录下。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9gh6i","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6h71i","text":"二. 需要配置的环境变量","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"88fu3","text":"1. PATH环境变量。作用是指定命令搜索路径，在shell下面执行命令时，它会到PATH变量所指定的路径中查找看是否能找到相应的命令程序。我们需要把 jdk安装目录下的bin目录增加到现有的PATH变量中，bin目录中包含经常要用到的可执行文件如javac/java/javadoc等待，设置好 PATH变量后，就可以在任何目录下执行javac/java等工具了。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2taq8","text":"2. CLASSPATH环境变量。作用是指定类搜索路径，要使用已经编写好的类，前提当然是能够找到它们了，JVM就是通过CLASSPTH来寻找类的。我们 需要把jdk安装目录下的lib子目录中的dt.jar和tools.jar设置到CLASSPATH中，当然，当前目录“.”也必须加入到该变量中。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4uebg","text":"3. JAVA_HOME环境变量。它指向jdk的安装目录，Eclipse/NetBeans/Tomcat等软件就是通过搜索JAVA_HOME变量来找到并使用安装好的jdk。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dn585","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6iged","text":"三. 三种配置环境变量的方法1. 修改/etc/profile文件","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5rqmh","text":"如果你的计算机仅仅作为开发使用时推荐使用这种方法，因为所有用户的shell都有权使用这些环境变量，可能会给系统带来安全性问题。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2q6b2","text":"·用文本编辑器打开/etc/profile","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"744je","text":"·在profile文件末尾加入：","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8galh","text":"export JAVA_HOME=/usr/share/jdk1.6.0_14","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2cvad","text":"export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cmi3e","text":"export CLASSPATH=.:$JAVA_HOME/lib/dt.jar:$JAVA_HOME/lib/tools.jar","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4du2t","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"973u2","text":"·重新登录","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"f2p5q","text":"·注解","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3h618","text":"a. 你要将 /usr/share/jdk1.6.0_14改为你的jdk安装目录","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a51ba","text":"b. linux下用冒号“:”来分隔路径","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5bf7r","text":"c. $PATH / $CLASSPATH / $JAVA_HOME 是用来引用原来的环境变量的值","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4l8vb","text":"在设置环境变量时特别要注意不能把原来的值给覆盖掉了，这是一种","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"kfvc","text":"常见的错误。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bv5b","text":"d. CLASSPATH中当前目录“.”不能丢,把当前目录丢掉也是常见的错误。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aftn6","text":"e. export是把这三个变量导出为全局变量。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fcjs6","text":"f. 大小写必须严格区分。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2h7ma","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1v56f","text":"2. 修改.bash_profile文件","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6mbtt","text":"ls -a 显示隐藏文件夹（bash_profile 是隐藏文件夹）","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9n6cq","text":"这种方法更为安全，它可以把使用这些环境变量的权限控制到用户级别，如果你需要给某个用户权限使用这些环境变量，你只需要修改其个人用户主目录下的.bash_profile文件就可以了。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6remc","text":"·用文本编辑器打开用户目录下的.bash_profile文件","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"83rg5","text":"·在.bash_profile文件末尾加入：","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8phkn","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"51a3q","text":"export JAVA_HOME=/usr/share/jdk1.6.0_14","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"25m3m","text":"export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"g96i","text":"export CLASSPATH=.:$JAVA_HOME/lib/dt.jar:$JAVA_HOME/lib/tools.jar","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2n2ld","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"80vfv","text":"·重新登录","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"44gt3","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bqdgp","text":"3. 直接在shell下设置变量","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2c62t","text":"不赞成使用这种方法，因为换个shell，你的设置就无效了，因此这种方法仅仅是临时使用，以后要使用的时候又要重新设置，比较麻烦。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"epk62","text":"只需在shell终端执行下列命令：","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"42sij","text":"export JAVA_HOME=/usr/share/jdk1.6.0_14","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6oibv","text":"export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"83ar8","text":"export CLASSPATH=.:$JAVA_HOME/lib/dt.jar:$JAVA_HOME/lib/tools.jar","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7nu8d","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cp712","text":"四. 测试jdk","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ur29","text":"1. 用文本编辑器新建一个Test.java文件，在其中输入以下代码并保存：","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d5fv3","text":"public class test {","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3q0eu","text":"public static void main(String args[]) {","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2ds3j","text":"System.out.println(\"A new jdk test !\");","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"f96iu","text":"}","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e9rvp","text":"}","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1mreb","text":"2. 编译：在shell终端执行命令 javac Test.java","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4tbdm","text":"3. 运行：在shell终端执行命令 java Test","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cnme5","text":"当shell下出现“A new jdk test !”字样则jdk运行正常。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4vj3n","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fk9nk","text":"五. 卸载jdk","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fpcnk","text":"·找到jdk安装目录的_uninst子目录","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dqidv","text":"·在shell终端执行命令./uninstall.sh即可卸载jdk。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},"dateCreated":"2017-11-28T04:47:24.780Z","lastUpdated":"2017-11-28T04:48:17.298Z","notebookId":"rJx8zxrxf"}
